<p>There are a few plugins that, with small visual cues, makes coding just a little bit easier. The ones I use right now:</p>

<p><strong>Bracket Pair Colorizer 2</strong>
This can help you udnerstand what is enclosed by what. It simplifies debugging as well as makes you more aware of potential mis-types as they happen. The plugin will color the opening and closing brackets that belong together in the same color:</p>

